                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer">Among common beverages, cold brew coffee has the highest caffeine per serving at around 200 mg per 12 oz. A standard shot of espresso has about 63 mg per 1 oz shot. Energy drinks like Bang and Reign contain 300 mg per can. Drip coffee averages 95 mg per 8 oz cup.</div>
